&lt;li id="fn2"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Okay, maybe not &lt;em&gt;literally&lt;/em&gt; every one. But, pretty much every one.&lt;a href="#fnref2" class="footnote-back"&gt;↩&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li id="fn3"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thank you based Hindley-Milner.&lt;a href="#fnref3" class="footnote-back"&gt;↩&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
